called damping constant. The noise is interpreted in the\nStratonovich sense. Given $T>0$, we will prove the existence of a martingale\nsolution on $[0,T]$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 29 Sep 2020 05:42:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-09-30"}
