d a spin coupled to a bosonic environment. We also discuss\na more general situation where $\\widetilde H = \\widetilde H_t$ is\ntime-dependent but dynamically integrable.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 29 Sep 2020 08:54:21 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 12 Oct 2020 07:50:25 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 2 Nov 2020 12:24:28 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Thu, 26 Nov 2020 08:01:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-08-04"}
