aar null).\n  Finally, in order to clarify the situation, we investigate the various\npossible definitions of singularity for maps of several variables, and explore\nthe connections between them.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 29 Sep 2020 15:42:37 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 24 Oct 2020 09:37:18 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 13 Apr 2021 17:19:59 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-11-22"}
